text: @ATTCares I ordered a phone for my friend nearly two weeks ago.  She still hasn't received it.  I talk to @UPSHelp and they say talk to @ATT.  I talk to @ATT, they tell me to talk to @UPS.  No one helps me, but they seem very positive that I will get my phone.

@jameshekel I understand your concern if you've not received your package. We'd be happy to help look into this with you. Please use the link to send us a DM. We'll need your tracking number, delivery address and phone number.  ^SK https://t.co/wKJHDXWGRQ
